{"tid":1349480,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【全民罷交稅】不合作運動應升級！","createTime":"2019-07-22T10:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T12:48:30.000Z","uid":67045,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e7d2d874093afb56d93042011071bc8eb965a2ba","tid":1349480,"uid":67045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:23:15.000Z","msg":"叫你地班港豬罷工都嘥9氣<br />\n<br />\n港鐵不合作運動<br />\n呼籲咗咁多次都無次夠人<br />\n<br />\n咁撚鐘意番工<br />\n你地唔會鐘意交稅掛？<br />\n<br />\n如果全港市民集體<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「收唔到稅單」，<br />\n唔知政府要告哂全香港要幾耐呢</span></span>？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n方法好簡單，只要收到稅單之後，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「唔知點解整唔見咗」</strong></span>，<br />\n等佢再寄封信吸催你交稅果陣，<br />\n<br />\n你再喺信後面寫住：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「我從來無收過稅單！係你地寄失咗！唔該寄過封俾我！」</span></span><br />\n如是者重覆兩三次，就已經會到下年！<br />\n<br />\n以政府派$4000既速度<br />\n相信全香港咁樣來回兩三次已經夠佢玩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望全港市民可以團結集體收唔到稅單！</span></span>"},{"pid":"be2e41aaa382c8bd07652e933eeec7b187e04fe2","tid":1349480,"uid":67045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:23:34.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"67ccfef213988189ce76294a5d73f36ed97e4d0b","tid":1349480,"uid":67045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:24:10.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"ae08eb2589e2002554b4cec24defb543a1bd746d","tid":1349480,"uid":67045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:24:20.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"00f5bbc5cc7e4b3f8e7d96162d0138c49f42af67","tid":1349480,"uid":253183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:24:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5