,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:34:20.000Z","msg":"你唔交稅 我ACO無糧出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌攬炒啦 我都唔撚交啦<br />\n一於全世界咪撚交 同林奠一鑊熟</span></span>"},{"pid":"1427a1a770f8cd988e96876051a1374578b9ac49","tid":1349480,"uid":67045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e7d2d874093afb56d93042011071bc8eb965a2ba","tid":1349480,"uid":67045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:23:15.000Z","msg":"叫你地班港豬罷工都嘥9氣<br />\n<br />\n港鐵不合作運動<br />\n呼籲咗咁多次都無次夠人<br />\n<br />\n咁撚鐘意番工<br />\n你地唔會鐘意交稅掛？<br />\n<br />\n如果全港市民集體<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「收唔到稅單」，<br />\n唔知政府要告哂全香港要幾耐呢</span></span>？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n方法好簡單，只要收到稅單之後，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「唔知點解整唔見咗」</strong></span>，<br />\n等佢再寄封信吸催你交稅果陣，<br />\n<br />\n你再喺信後面寫住：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「我從來無收過稅單！係你地寄失咗！唔該寄過封俾我！」</span></span><br />\n如是者重覆兩三次，就已經會到下年！<br />\n<br />\n以政府派$4000既速度<br />\n相信全香港咁樣來回兩三次已經夠佢玩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望全港市民可以團結集體收唔到稅單！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:41:50.000Z","msg":"Sorry再講清楚少少<br />\n如果你「整唔見稅單」<br />\n政府再寄封咁既信俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPH031W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPH031W.png&h=2a7dbc22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要你喺呢封信後面寫住：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">致稅務局局長：<br />\n<br />\n本人xxx身份證xxx於x年x月x日前，從未收過稅單，煩請重新寄出副本</span></span><br />\n<br />\n之後將信寄出，完成<br />\n<br />\n如果擔心唔夠安全<br />\n可以打埋去稅局，屌9個職員<br />\n<br />\n建議台詞：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">「我屌你老母啊？<br />\n無啦啦寄封信嚟催我交稅？<br />\n我從來無收過稅單！<br />\n肯定係你地寫錯我地址寄撚失咗啦！<br />\n$4000唔見你派你催我交稅？<br />\n嗱，我同你講，一係你重新寄過俾我！」</span></span>"},{"pid":"61b30e91b9491f8b98891f12ddadd81b42c21e42","tid":1349480,"uid":67045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:42:39.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"07530aa12027c8a2b34257a99ef386e6b25a076b","tid":1349480,"uid":67045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:43:42.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"18afc55f89f4c8462b086c51e8e31ec102b64216","tid":1349480,"uid":67045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:44:05.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"b6411b4ffc3dfeb5f77e5899631e0ebd219a8b43","tid":1349480,"uid":67045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:50:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5f5112ecb0e52d1de58928a4fecd248c7a1636c","tid":1349480,"uid":67045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:50:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc41700f2327c18f8c70badc4c42cfa30427d800","tid":1349480,"uid":263577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:59:11.000Z","msg":"歡迎政府停擺，寧願用稅金組成基金去支持返公共醫療、市政、消防等真正有需要的社會功能。<br />\n架空政府法律唔容許? 公職人員不能接受民間資金? ICAC仲存在既咩？當政府失去其正當性，當政府都視法治、自治如無物既時候，法律亦都失去要遵守既理由。<br />\n政府拒絕去做既野，由其他人去做，權力亦自然轉移到其他肯承擔起責任的人。"},{"pid":"fc70ac18dbb8c8b160222eefff31d508679760c7","tid":1349480,"uid":67045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:00:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全民自發救港<br />\n不交稅、不養警狗<br />\n市民憤怒了</span>"},{"pid":"62144ad9519ca12f9b3c6ab0b8e7085168833e1e","tid":1349480,"uid":284429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:04:03.000Z","msg":"「光復香港！時代革命！」"}]}